---
title: Smokey Baked Chicken with Feta Oregano Potatoes & Slaw
description: We can’t decide which we like best in this dish - the succulent chicken, corn-studded slaw or oregano potato wedges topped with creamy feta. We’ll leave it up to you, but don’t be shy about agreeing that every element is hard to beat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5cee38ccd1df710016523fad-1cfcec72.jpg
